data.description:
****Multiple Offers Highest and Best Due Tuesday 4/16/2024 by 5:00PM**** 
Seize the chance to own this remarkable 3+ bedroom, 2-bath home with a 2-car attached garage, and extra kitchenette in lower level nestled on an exceptional lot. Boasting Granite Counters, a spacious deck, fenced-in yard, shed, and newer washer/dryer, it also features a sprinkler system and Kinetico Water System for added convenience. Enjoy breathtaking sunsets with the city-owned land parcel adjacent, enhancing the picturesque setting. Conveniently located near Hwy 169, 610 Freeway, and Hwy 10, this home offers both tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
